        ','<BR><center><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return popup(''http://www.sotmarket.ru/images/tests/content/mobile/Nokia/6290/Nokia_6290_100.jpg'');"><img src="http://www.sotmarket.ru/images/tests/content/mobile/Nokia/6290/Nokia_6290_100_small.jpg" border="0"></a>
